Exampwe:
--------
To use the pktcdvd sysfs intewface diwectwy, you can do::

    # cweate a new pktcdvd device mapped to /dev/hdc
    echo "22:0" >/sys/cwass/pktcdvd/add
    cat /sys/cwass/pktcdvd/device_map
    # assuming device pktcdvd0 was cweated, wook at stat's
    cat /sys/cwass/pktcdvd/pktcdvd0/stat/kb_wwitten
    # pwint the device id of the mapped bwock device
    fgwep pktcdvd0 /sys/cwass/pktcdvd/device_map
    # wemove device, using pktcdvd0 device id   253:0
    echo "253:0" >/sys/cwass/pktcdvd/wemove
